8. QA visual comparison.

## 17. Project-Specific Risk Matrix
**Purpose**: Identifying fault points upfront.
| Risk | Root Cause | Validation / Prevention |
| ---- | ---------- | ----------------------- |
| Mesh Background Drift | Dropping complex `inline style` properties or `rgb` overlaps | Ensure strict parsing of `style={{ ... }}` objects to html attributes. |
| Mega Menu Hover failure | Lack of `useEffect` to manage `click-outside` state | Build bulletproof window listener `event.target.closest('[data-menu-trigger]')` |
| Font loading failure | Forgetting to map GCP buckets in Global CSS | Explicit `<style>` copy step in `head` element generation. |
| Form state lockups | Loss of controlled input states `value={var}` in React | Basic vanilla DOM binding via `getElementById()`. |

## 18. Definition of Done
**Sign Off Gate:**
- 11 Explicit pages served statically via discrete `index.html` files.
- ZERO reliance on React, React-DOM, Remix, Next, Vite Dev Servers.
- 100% component equivalence verifiable by side-by-side overlay comparison.
- All CTA links functioning.
- Tailwind class utilities compiling effectively.
